Facebook post by Noorie Noor Ananta, 8 November 2016, 'is feeling awesome.' Text: 'Good job' with thumbs up and wink emojis. Image shows a large scorpion illustration with giant number '8' against dramatic sky with sun rays. THE REVEAL: Posted on the actual day of demonetization. 'Good job' + 'feeling awesome' = celebration/vindication of the prediction. Scorpion + 8 = the code she had been posting for weeks, now fulfilled. Sun rays = divine truth revealed. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Coded Signals — the moment of prophecy fulfilment.